    "body": "probably something like:\n\n```\nio obj failure_guard(chan[tid] c) {  \n    drop {\n        if (sys.failing()) {\n            c <| sys.gettid();\n            sys.flush(c);\n        }\n    }\n}\n\nfn trap(chan[tid] c, (fn () -> ()) thunk) {\n  auto guard = failure_guard(c);\n  sys.unlink();\n  thunk();\n}\n```\n\nwill do.\n",
